org.wonderly.jini.entry
Class DesktopEntry

java.lang.Object
  org.wonderly.jini.entry.DesktopEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Entry
public class DesktopEntry
extends Object
implements Entry

This Entry is used to specify an icon that would appear on a 'desktop' to activate a particular serviceUI role. it identifies a grouping, the role, the icon, and an indication of whether the service is transient to help a desktop understand whether it can depend on this mapping to be around for any length of time.

Author:
Gregg Wonderly - gregg.wonderly@pobox.com
